      • self

        private FormalParam self
        Create a new FormalParam object for the shadow parameter "self". This object will be referred by the self symbol in this method. Do not add it to the parameters list.

      • returnTypeData

        private Type returnTypeData
        A reference to the type of the value returned by the method. This can be
      • Program.intType - for Int parameters
      • An LCPLClass - for class parameters
      • Program.noType - for methods that do not return any type
